v8:item.v8:content: Group this contract is included to.
Contract description. Is required for the prompt visual contract identification during the work with the application.
Company, the contract is concluded with. Attribute is used only for the data exchange with the "Enterprise Accounting" configuration.
Shows the contract settlements in standard units
Customer payment delay period is set if the contract provides an individual payment deadline that differs from the payment deadline specified in the accounting settings.
Vendor payment delay period is set if the contract provides an individual payment deadline that differs from the payment deadline specified in the accounting setings.
Type of the contract with the counterparty. Attribute is used only for the data exchange with the "Enterprise Accounting" configuration.
Type of the prices which will be automatically filled in the documents for the goods, works and services realization when selecting the counterparty contract.
Type of the prices which will be automatically filled in the documents for the goods and services purchase of the third party companies when selecting the counterparty contract.
Type of the applied discount which will be automatically filled in the documents for the realization of goods, works and services in case of selection of the counterparty contract.
